<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Diecz, als her Wirich
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>biss<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan>, nehst <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ew geredt hat, daz ir ew
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>anneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wöllet <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frawn
                            <expan>Kathr<ex>ein</ex></expan>
<expan>Czolln<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, und
                            <expan>Görge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Tanne von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nam
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czü Geyselwinden, hat uns her
                            <expan>Wirich</expan> gesagt, daz ir <expan>gesproche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, ir wöllet ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unt<ex>er</ex>winde<ex>n</ex></expan>, wenn wir ew selber <pb facs="#facs_161" id="80r"/><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                                <expan>anneme<ex>n</ex></expan> und des <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet,
                        darauf sie <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wil; und lazzet ew das
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>empfolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, also daz des
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan> kurzlich ein awstrag
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> xi
                                <expan>miliu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>ir</ex>ginu<ex>m</ex></expan>.</ab>
